<br>
Quote:<br>
<br>
&quot;We dont have anything to gain from reputation since were already at the top. What would it do us to be considered good guys? You want a good reputation when you want peoples to like you. We dont care much about being liked or not. Well still win that race in the end....&quot;<br>
<br>
That pretty much says it all and is proof of how your guild carries out business day to day.  And your illogic gives you a &quot;barrier&quot; to hide behind.  Its the &quot;well we are already deemed bad guys lets just act like it&quot;  syndrome.  If you are so short sighted that you can't see the basic complaint....<br>
<br>
What the other guilds are saying is that they CHOOSE not to behave like you do. They choose not to display the attitude your guild does. You don't think COP couldn't roll over a few DH raids if we chose to???? You are naive. You don't think COP (or someone else for that matter) couldn't just &quot;win the race&quot; if it was all that mattered and how we played the game?<br>
<br>
Its not about winning the race man. Unfortunately that is what your guild thinks this game is all about.  That is how your guild conducts its business.  Your comments directly reflect your guild's apparent indifference to the rest of the server. It has managed to alienate you guys to the point where you don't understand anything else that is going on. <br>
<br>
How can you guys enjoy all the loot and accomplishments when no one else cares??  When your guild is loathed instead of admired.  <br>
<br>
Thats why I call you bush league.<br>
<br>
Any guild can so choose to behave like a collective pack of idiots.  The rest of the server just chooses to be human and play like there is other humans on the other end.  You guys have only focused on the &quot;ends&quot; and abused the &quot;means&quot; to get there.<br>
<br>
And that is the point of this thread.<br>
<br>
WINNING THE RACE?  C'mon man, that is OLD EQ!!!!!<br>
<br>
Now we have so many worthy guilds, and servers, and Legends... &quot;winning the race&quot; is so tired.....so old....and you guys can't see that. <br>
<br>
You would rather hog the AOW then let someone have a legitimate shot. You would rather leapfrog over COP to the Creator so you can deny for the sake of denying. Your ill-will toward others and only the &quot;means&quot; to the end and only &quot;winning the race&quot; is all you can see.<br>
<br>
And that is bush league in my book.<br>
<br>
And the only thing that reasonably holds you guys in check is threads like these. <br>
<br>
Daneric<br>
